@GrkStav @RaulACarrillo You’re right, in terms of #MonetaryRate policy, options are:
1. raise interest rates
2. maintain interest rates
3. lower interest rates
4. announce / telegraph / threaten to do one of the above three things for some period of time
5. make a habit of doing #4, then say nothing

@GrkStav @RaulACarrillo Now, perhaps monetary rate policy isn’t the ideal tool (now? sometimes? ever?);

there are a whole host of other policy options (some politically unavailable at present),

some of which are only theory and some which have been proven by time.

#Economics is a young art.

